sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor ScannerA as Staff Device A
    actor ScannerB as Staff Device B
    participant Verify as Verification Orchestrator
    participant Redis as Redis Lock
    participant Ticket as Ticket Service

    par First scan
        ScannerA->>Verify: POST /verify/scan
        Verify->>Redis: SET scan_lock:{ticketId} NX EX 5
        Redis-->>Verify: lock granted
        Verify->>Ticket: continue verification
        Ticket-->>Verify: ticket details
        Verify-->>ScannerA: 200 or 409 based on ticket state
        Verify->>Redis: release lock by token
    and Second scan at same time
        ScannerB->>Verify: POST /verify/scan
        Verify->>Redis: SET scan_lock:{ticketId} NX EX 5
        Redis-->>Verify: lock busy
        Verify-->>ScannerB: 409 concurrent scan
    end
